high_descs: Turn to your left, move forward then turn left and head to the side table
Pick up the figurine on the side table
Turn to your right make a step then face the lamp
anns.task_desc: Examine the figurine by the light

high_descs: Turn around and go to the small rectangle black table at the far side of the room.
Pick up the statue from the table.
Take the statue, and look to the right to see the lamp.
Hold the statue, and turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Picking up a statue and then turning the lamp on.

high_descs: Turn around and walk by the couch to the black end table next to the piano.
Pick up the sculpture next to the remote.
Move in front of the lamp on the right and lift up the sculpture to the lamp.
Use the sculpture to turn the lamp on.
anns.task_desc: To turn on the lamp with the sculpture.
